   h. Defense. E: 27. G: 45. F: 18. P 8. DK-NA: 4.
   i. Relations with the Soviet Union. E: 36. G: 46. F: 13. P: 3.
DK-NA: 3.
   j. Other foreign policy. E: 13. G: 45. F: 29. P: 7. DK-NA: 5.
   k. Appointments of federal judges. E: 7. G: 36. F: 32. P: 16.
